org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver

类 CellArrayImmutableSegment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.Segment
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.ImmutableSegment
        • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.CellArrayImmutableSegment
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    MemStoreSizing

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class CellArrayImmutableSegment
extends ImmutableSegment
    CellArrayImmutableSegment extends the API supported by a Segment, and ImmutableSegment. This immutable segment is working with CellSet with CellArrayMap delegatee.
